I'm flirting with the edge of insanity, Dismayed by the notion of all doubt, And numbers continue to destroy me, Like the devil whose flames won't die out...

For 23 Days... I will isolate myself, to the best of my abilities, from Packer society. I will avoid all instances of distraction. I will stay focused. I will believe. I will relive my freshman and sophmore year. I will put my life on hold. I will put secondary priorities on hold. I will wake up at 6 am. I will stay motivated. I will master you. I will eat, sleep and dream you. And, in 23 days... I will vehemently destroy you.
